---
// HowItWorks — static landing-page section
---

<section class="how-it-works">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Three steps from detection to resolution</p>
  </div>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">1</div>
      <div class="step-icon">📡</div>
      <h3 class="step-title">Monitor</h3>
      <p class="step-description">SWE Squad continuously monitors your GitHub repositories for new issues. It triages incoming bugs and feature requests automatically, assigning severity and module tags.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step-connector" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="connector-arrow">&#8250;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">2</div>
      <div class="step-icon">🔍</div>
      <h3 class="step-title">Investigate</h3>
      <p class="step-description">Each issue gets a dedicated AI agent that deeply investigates the root cause. The agent reads code, checks git history, and identifies affected files before planning a fix.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step-connector" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="connector-arrow">&#8250;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">3</div>
      <div class="step-icon">🔧</div>
      <h3 class="step-title">Fix</h3>
      <p class="step-description">The agent implements the fix, runs tests, and submits a pull request. A stability gate ensures only passing fixes are merged, keeping your main branch green.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    --color-bg: #0d1117;
    --color-surface: #161b22;
    --color-border: #30363d;
    --color-text: #e6edf3;
    --color-text-secondary: #8b949e;
    --color-accent: #7c3aed;
    --color-accent-light: #a78bfa;

    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  /* ---- Section header ---- */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ---- Steps row ---- */
  .steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 0;
  }

  /* ---- Individual step card ---- */
  .step {
    flex: 1 1 0;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .step-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .step-description {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ---- Connector between steps ---- */
  .step-connector {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 3rem;
    min-width: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-connector::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  .connector-arrow {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    color: var(--color-border);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1;
    padding: 0 0.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ---- Responsive: stack vertically on small screens ---- */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .how-it-works {
      padding: 2rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .steps {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .step {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .step-connector {
      width: auto;
      min-width: auto;
      height: 2.5rem;
      min-height: 2.5rem;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .step-connector::before {
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 50%;
      right: auto;
      width: 2px;
      height: 100%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }

    .connector-arrow {
      padding: 0.25rem 0;
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
